metadata.name: Artemis
metadata.description:
Artemis is the Olympian goddess of the hunt, the moon, and chastity. She was the patron and protector of young children and women. Her special powers include perfect aim with the bow and arrow the ability to turn herself and others into animals, healing, disease, and control of nature.
